lead_paragraph: MANHATTAN, Kan. (AP) — Take it back to the beginning, all the way to the womb. The baby is two weeks late, probably laughing from inside his mother while everyone waits for him to come out. When he does, it is at a whopping 10 pounds 9 ounces, and 23 inches long.
